# PokemonYellowRecomp — .gitignore
# RULE: never commit copyrighted ROMs or anything derived that contains them.
# A BPS patch contains ONLY our added content (diff), not the ROM — it is safe
# to ship/commit. Built ROMs, saves with ROM-derived data, and generated/build
# trees are all excluded.

# --- ROMs (copyrighted — users supply their own) ---
*.gb
*.gbc
*.sgb
roms/

# --- third-party build deps (cloned/submodule'd, not vendored) ---
pokeyellow/
pokecrystal/
tools/rgbds/

# --- recompiler output + native build trees ---
recomp/
recomp_stock/
*.o
*.obj
*.2bpp
*.pic
*.sym
*.map

# --- runtime/user state ---
*.sav
*.rtc
*.state*
rom.cfg
runtime_prefs.ini
imgui.ini
keybinds.ini
logs/
*.ppm
*.log

# --- scratch ---
*_preview.png
src_back.png
back_nearest.png


# third-party tool archives (RGBDS prebuilt) — not vendored
tools/*.zip
# scratch screenshots
rekey_frame.png
*_frame.png

# No distributable artifacts in the repo. A BPS diff still encodes the
# Crystal-derived (copyrighted) content we add, so it is NOT shipped either —
# the ROM is built locally from pret. Track scripts/docs only.
dist/
__pycache__/
# launcher build artifacts (built locally from launcher/yellow.c)
/yellow.exe
/yellow.cfg

# regenerated recomp output + pre-launcher backup (build trees)
pokeyellow_recomp_output/
pokeyellow_recomp_output_pre_launcher/
